<template><div><h4 id="_79-单词搜索" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_79-单词搜索" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/word-search/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">79. 单词搜索<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h4>
<p>难度中等1434</p>
<p>给定一个 <code v-pre>m x n</code> 二维字符网格 <code v-pre>board</code> 和一个字符串单词 <code v-pre>word</code> 。如果 <code v-pre>word</code> 存在于网格中，返回 <code v-pre>true</code> ；否则，返回 <code v-pre>false</code> 。</p>
<p>单词必须按照字母顺序，通过相邻的单元格内的字母构成，其中“相邻”单元格是那些水平相邻或垂直相邻的单元格。同一个单元格内的字母不允许被重复使用。</p>
<p><strong>示例 1：</strong></p>
<figure><img src="https://assets.leetcode.com/uploads/2020/11/04/word2.jpg" alt="img" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>img</figcaption></figure>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>输入：board = [["A","B","C","E"],["S","F","C","S"],["A","D","E","E"]], word = "ABCCED"
输出：true
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>示例 2：</strong></p>
<figure><img src="https://assets.leetcode.com/uploads/2020/11/04/word-1.jpg" alt="img" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>img</figcaption></figure>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>输入：board = [["A","B","C","E"],["S","F","C","S"],["A","D","E","E"]], word = "SEE"
输出：true
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>示例 3：</strong></p>
<figure><img src="https://assets.leetcode.com/uploads/2020/10/15/word3.jpg" alt="img" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>img</figcaption></figure>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="language-text"><code>输入：board = [["A","B","C","E"],["S","F","C","S"],["A","D","E","E"]], word = "ABCB"
输出：false
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>提示：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code v-pre>m == board.length</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>n = board[i].length</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>1 &lt;= m, n &lt;= 6</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>1 &lt;= word.length &lt;= 15</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>board</code> 和 <code v-pre>word</code> 仅由大小写英文字母组成</li>
</ul>
